 e to study and live freely like we do today. Join us for trivia to test y
 our knowledge and win some cute prizes. All Indiana University events\, g
 roups\, activities\, educational\, cultural\, and historical observances 
 welcome all IU students and other members of the Indiana University commu
 nity. \n\nHosted by: Culture of Care\n\nAdditional Information can be fou
 nd at: https://beinvolved.indiana.edu/event/12321107
