 e Intimate Animal: The Science of Sex\, Fidelity\, and Why we Live and Di
 e for Love. The lecture will be followed by a Q&A\, book signing\, and re
 ception!  This event is in partnership with the IU Bookstore.\nCompliment
 ary food and free book giveaway included!\n6pm - Lecture in Tudor Room\nB
 ook signing in IU Bookstore following the lecture\nAll Indiana University
  events\, groups\, activities\, and educational\, cultural\, and historic
 al observances welcome all IU students and other members of the Indiana U
 niversity community.\n\nHosted by: Indiana Memorial Union Board\n\nAdditi
 onal Information can be found at: https://beinvolved.indiana.edu/event/12
 365321
