DESCRIPTION:Reintroducing Go Game at ACC! Interested in learning the ancie
 nt board game Go? Whether you've never picked up a stone or only know the
  basics\, our Go club is the perfect place to start. With generous help f
 rom our volunteer\, Tyler Stoner\, we welcome players of all ages and bac
 kgrounds to explore this fascinating game of territory\, tactics and intu
 ition. No experience is necessary\, just curiosity and willingness to lea
 rn!   \n \nAll Indiana University events\, groups\, activities\, and educ
 ational\, cultural\, and historical observances welcome all IU students a
 nd other members of the Indiana University community.\n\nHosted by: Asian
  Culture Center\n\nAdditional Information can be found at: https://beinvo
 lved.indiana.edu/event/11993422
