CATEGORIES:Arts
CATEGORIES:Dance
CATEGORIES:Performance
DESCRIPTION:Keep It Classic is a collaborative dance showcase that brings 
 together the elegance of Western ballet and the expressive depth of India
 n classical dance. Co-hosted by Nrithya @ IU and Jacobs Ballet\, the perf
 ormance highlights each tradition’s unique artistry while exploring momen
 ts of harmony through original choreography. Keep It Classic celebrates t
 he power of tradition\, the beauty of contrast\, and the universal langua
 ge of movement that connects dancers and audiences across cultures.\n\nHo
 sted by: Nrithya at IU\n\nAdditional Information can be found at: https:/
 /beinvolved.indiana.edu/event/12319409
