DESCRIPTION:The Social Media Marketing Club is a student-run organization 
 at Indiana University focused on hands-on learning in digital marketing\,
  branding\, and content creation. SMMC provides members with real-world e
 xperience by working on campaigns for student organizations and local bus
 inesses\, hosting workshops\, running design and strategy sprints\, and b
 uilding a collaborative community for aspiring marketers. Our mission is 
 to help students develop practical creative\, strategic\, and leadership 
 skills that prepare them for careers in media\, advertising\, and marketi
 ng.\n\nHosted by: Social Media Marketing Club\n\nAdditional Information c
 an be found at: https://beinvolved.indiana.edu/event/11936348
