DESCRIPTION:Ballot vs. Bullet is an interactive event that explores the po
 wer of voting versus more radical forms of resistance in the fight for Bl
 ack rights and social change. Inspired by Malcom Xs famous speech\, parti
 cipants will step into the roles of historical figures and engage in disc
 ussions\, debates\, and scenarios that highlight different approaches to 
 achieving justice. This event encourages critical thinking about civic en
 gagement\, activism\, and the impact of political participation in shapin
 g our com\n\nHosted by: The Pre Black Law Students Association \n\nAdditi
 onal Information can be found at: https://beinvolved.indiana.edu/event/12
