 idarity. Interactive activity and refreshments provided. Co-hosted: OSVPV
 A and La Casa.\nAll Indiana University events\, groups\, activities\, edu
 cational\, cultural\, and historical observances welcome all IU students 
 and other members of the Indiana University community.\n\nHosted by: La C
 asa/Latino Cultural Center\, Office for Sexual Violence Prevention and Vi
 ctim Advocacy\n\nAdditional Information can be found at: https://beinvolv
 ed.indiana.edu/event/12239398
