BEGIN:VEVENT
X-SOURCE:IU beINvolved Student Orgs
CATEGORIES:ThoughtfulLearning
CATEGORIES:Emotional Wellness
DESCRIPTION:The intent behind this movie night is to spread awareness abou
 t the difficulties of seasons and changes in life. Through the many theme
 s throughout this movie\, it shines a light on what it means to be yourse
 lf. As we go onwards from the season of April to May\, many things change
  and grow.  Embracing who you are while still figuring out who you are is
  okay. It’s okay to not be okay and it’s okay to accept the love you dese
 rve. This movie also highlights past trauma and how it doesn’t define who
  you are\, but recognizing it can help you grow further through the upcom
 ing seasons.\nResearch: “A number of research (e.g.\, Rodríguez et al.\, 
 2008\; Tinsley & Eldredge\, 1995) has shown that participation in leisure
  activities contributes to life satisfaction and SWB (Social Well Being).
 ..Studies have shown that leisure participation influences SWB via leisur
 e satisfaction based on psychological need theory and bottom-up models of
  SWB (Kuykendallet al.\, 2015). Walker and Kono (2018) found that satisfa
 ction of psychological needs for autonomy\, competence\, and relatedness 
 positively affected leisure domain satisfaction\, which in turn positivel
 y influenced global life satisfaction.”\nKim\, D.\, Park\, J.\, & Park\, 
 B. (2024). How do leisure activities impact leisure domain and life domai
 n satisfaction and subjective well‐being? International Journal of Touris
 m Research\, 26(1). https://doi.org/10.1002/jtr.2618\n\nHosted by: U Brin
 g Change to Mind\n\nAdditional Information can be found at: https://beinv
 olved.indiana.edu/event/12380717
DTEND:20260409T000000Z
DTSTAMP:20260331T050034Z
DTSTART:20260408T220000Z
LOCATION:Ballantine Hall\, BLBH 330
SEQUENCE:0
STATUS:CONFIRMED
SUMMARY:The Perks Of Being A Wallflower
UID:https://beinvolved.indiana.edu/event/12380717
URL:https://beinvolved.indiana.edu/event/12380717
X-HOSTS:U Bring Change to Mind
END:VEVENT
