DESCRIPTION:Join us for the Student Involvement and Leadership Center's Le
 adership Compass Series\, a monthly leadership development series designe
 d to help students grow across the 8 Student Leadership Competency domain
 s. Each session will focus on one core leadership area—ranging from self-
 awareness to civic responsibility—through interactive workshops and hands
 -on activities. This 8-workshop series (spanning the academic year) provi
 des a dynamic space for students to build confidence\, sharpen their skil
 ls\, and connect with peers who are passionate about personal and communi
 ty growth.\nWhether you're new to leadership or already involved on campu
 s\, the SILC Leadership Compass offers practical tools and meaningful con
 versations to elevate your leadership journey—one domain at a time.\n \n*
 **Lunch is provided for participants from 12:00pm-1:00pm on all dates***\
 n \n<!--StartFragment -->\n📅 April 11th\, 2026⏰ 10:00 AM – 3:00 PM📍 IMU
  Club Hub\n💡 Strong leadership requires adaptability—but how do leaders 
 make informed decisions and continuously grow? In "Learning and Reasoning
 \," the final event in the Leadership Compass Series\, we’ll explore the 
 Learning and Reasoning domain of the Student Leadership Competencies\, eq
 uipping you with the tools 🧠 to think critically\, evaluate information\
 , and approach problem-solving with confidence and clarity.\n🔥 Great lea
 ders never stop learning—let’s refine how you process information and mak
 e strategic decisions!\nAll Indiana University events\, groups\, activiti
 es\, and educational\, cultural\, and historical observances welcome all 
 IU students and other members of the Indiana University community.\n<!--E
 ndFragment -->\n\nHosted by: Student Involvement and Leadership Center\n\
 nAdditional Information can be found at: https://beinvolved.indiana.edu/e
 vent/11321024
DTEND:20260411T190000Z
DTSTAMP:20260331T050034Z
DTSTART:20260411T140000Z
LOCATION:IMU Club Hub
SEQUENCE:0
STATUS:CONFIRMED
SUMMARY:SILC Leadership Compass Series - "Learning and Reasoning"
UID:https://beinvolved.indiana.edu/event/11321024
URL:https://beinvolved.indiana.edu/event/11321024
X-HOSTS:Student Involvement and Leadership Center
END:VEVENT
