DESCRIPTION:\n\nAmerican Medical Women's Association (AMWA) holds biweekly
  General Body meetings where we offer updates on various volunteer opport
 unities\, professional workshops\, skill-building activities\, and commun
 ity connection for aspiring healthcare professionals.\n\n\n\nHosted by: A
