DESCRIPTION:Join us as we learn to cook a delicious dish called Pollo Salt
 ado.  Pollo Saltado\, a traditional Peruvian chicken stir-fry dish\, is a
  fusion meal influenced by Chinese immigration\, making it a ‘Chifa.’ Per
 uvian cuisine has been greatly influenced and inspired by Chinese immigra
 nts who came to Peru in the 1800s.\n\nHosted by: La Casa/Latino Cultural 
 Center\n\nAdditional Information can be found at: https://beinvolved.indi
