DESCRIPTION:Join us for the CRC Week Celebration as we come together to re
 cognize the importance of collegiate recovery and the impact it has on st
 udent success\, wellness\, and belonging. Collegiate Recovery provides st
 udents with supportive\, substance-free spaces where they can thrive acad
 emically\, socially\, and personally while pursuing their recovery.\nThis
  celebration is an opportunity for the campus community to learn more abo
 ut recovery\, reduce stigma\, and show support for students in all stages
  of their journey. Whether you’re part of the recovery community\, an all
 y\, or simply curious\, you’re invited to celebrate with us.\nEnjoy free 
 food\, yard games\, and CRC swag while connecting with others and celebra
 ting recovery\, resilience\, and community\n\nHosted by: Collegiate Recov
 ery Community\n\nAdditional Information can be found at: https://beinvolv
 ed.indiana.edu/event/12165652
DTEND:20260417T203000Z
DTSTAMP:20260331T050034Z
DTSTART:20260417T193000Z
LOCATION:Wellness House Lawn
SEQUENCE:0
STATUS:CONFIRMED
SUMMARY:CRC Week Celebration
