DESCRIPTION:This event will spotlight the Veggie Meter. A device that meas
 ures the amount of carotenoids in a person's in a person's skin to estima
 te their consumption of fruits and vegetables. The machine generates a "s
 core" by using reflection spectroscopy to measure carotenoid pigments by 
 scanning the tip of the finger.  It takes less than a minute to do.\n\nHo
 sted by: Health Promotion\n\nAdditional Information can be found at: http
 s://beinvolved.indiana.edu/event/12382234
