DESCRIPTION:Paint the Semester Away is an amazing paint and sip event for 
 students to celebrate the end of the semester and wind down before finals
  week. We'll have various items for students to paint\, including canvase
 s\, tote bags\, and trinket trays\, along with charcuterie and mocktails!
 \n6pm-8pm:  Special limited supply painting options to include wooden tra
 ys\, coasters\, tote bags\, etc. 9-12 during Almost Midnight Breakfast: C
 anvases available to pain\nAll Indiana University events\, groups\, activ
 ities\, and educational\, cultural\, and historical observances welcome a
 ll IU students and other members of the Indiana University community.\n\n
