DESCRIPTION:Join Union Board for it's traditional Almost Midnight Breakfas
 t featuring breakfast from IHOP\, live music\, crafts and so much more fu
 n. Enjoy tarot readings\, a chance to by hypnotized by a world renowned h
 ypnotist\, and more. Also get a chance to meet IU faculty and staff who a
 re rooting for your success in finals.  RSVP for faster check-in!\nRSVP d
 oes not guarantee you will have breakfast at your arrival time. Time slot
 s are allotted at the door\, first come\, first serve. Get here early and
  enjoy the activities before your breakfast time slot or get an early tim
 e slot when you arrive and stay after to play.\nAll Indiana University ev
 ents\, groups\, activities\, and educational\, cultural\, and historical 
 observances welcome all IU students and other members of the Indiana Univ
 ersity community.\n\nHosted by: Indiana Memorial Union Board\n\nAdditiona
 l Information can be found at: https://beinvolved.indiana.edu/event/12334
 861
