DESCRIPTION:\nIndiana University Bloomington’s LGBTQ+ Culture Center invit
 es you to the 2026 Lavender Celebration\, honoring the achievements of LG
 BTQ+ graduates and their guests.\n\n\n\n\nDate: Tuesday\, May 5\, 2026\n\
 n\nTime: 5–6:30 p.m.\n\n\nLocation: IMU Georgian Room\n\n\nIf you are gra
 duating in 2026\, you are warmly invited to participate in the ceremony a
 nd be recognized for your accomplishments. Graduating students are welcom
 e to invite family\, friends\, and supporters to share in this special oc
 casion.\nIf you are a graduating student\, a guest of a graduate\, or a g
 uest of the LGBTQ+ Culture Center\, please RSVP by 5 p.m. on Monday\, Apr
 il 21 using the registration link below: \nhttps://iu.co1.qualtrics.com/j
 fe/form/SV_eLO6sczbB3hSdj8\nAll Indiana University events\, groups\, acti
 vities\, and educational\, cultural\, and historical observances welcome 
 all IU students and other members of the Indiana University community.\nJ
 oin us as we celebrate community\, resilience\, and pride at IU Bloomingt
 on’s 2026 Lavender Celebration.\n\n\nHosted by: LGBTQ+ Culture Center\n\n
 Additional Information can be found at: https://beinvolved.indiana.edu/ev
 ent/12173071
DTEND:20260505T223000Z
DTSTAMP:20260331T050034Z
DTSTART:20260505T210000Z
LOCATION:IMU Georgian Room
SEQUENCE:0
STATUS:CONFIRMED
SUMMARY:Lavender Celebration 2026
UID:https://beinvolved.indiana.edu/event/12173071
URL:https://beinvolved.indiana.edu/event/12173071
X-HOSTS:LGBTQ+ Culture Center
